oscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b76e603c556114aa97c2af769b0b904f_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"1072\" data-rawheight=\"1268\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-fe95256ef3eeed7009e106e387d8470e\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b76e603c556114aa97c2af769b0b904f_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1072\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b76e603c556114aa97c2af769b0b904f_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1072&#39; height=&#39;1268&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1072\" data-rawheight=\"1268\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-fe95256ef3eeed7009e106e387d8470e\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b76e603c556114aa97c2af769b0b904f_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1072\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b76e603c556114aa97c2af769b0b904f_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b76e603c556114aa97c2af769b0b904f_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/><figcaption>图片来源于网络</figcaption></figure><p data-pid=\"NeAVk4u-\">豆瓣链接：</p><a data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//m.douban.com/book/subject/25836270/\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">m.douban.com/book/subje</span><span class=\"invisible\">ct/25836270/</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a><p data-pid=\"-e8LbePu\">不希望自己是女性也不希望自己是男性一点都不奇怪，本质上是对传统社会性别二元对立给现代人们戴上的枷锁的一种反抗意识。这本书中也提到了男性的“自我厌恶”。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-57383db345704d8a414bced86e2c8f70_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"968\" data-rawheight=\"559\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-bfbd91a1f59ee8a143540969ffa1a7ff\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-57383db345704d8a414bced86e2c8f70_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"968\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-57383db345704d8a414bced86e2c8f70_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;968&#39; height=&#39;559&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"968\" data-rawheight=\"559\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-bfbd91a1f59ee8a143540969ffa1a7ff\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-57383db345704d8a414bced86e2c8f70_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"968\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-57383db345704d8a414bced86e2c8f70_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-57383db345704d8a414bced86e2c8f70_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><p data-pid=\"J23riPss\">最后，本人不赞同任何轻易鼓励他人进行药物或手术变性的行为。性别厌恶（包括对男性身份和女性身份的厌恶）根源在于社会问题，解决方法需要每个人心态上的调整和对传统社会性别秩序的反抗。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><hr/><p data-pid=\"pGNzLOdz\">以下是关于跨性别的另一篇回答。希望对你有所帮助。</p><a data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/401462456/answer/1693787566\" class=\"internal\">为什么会有跨性别者的产生呢?</a><p></p>",
